metadata.name: Snow Rabbit (Lucky Edition)
metadata.description:
Happy New Year! This is a Thank You stamp exclusively given out to anyone who minted "Winter Apple" from Risu's "彼女の季節 (kanojo no kisetsu)" or "Her Season" series.

As a token of appreciation, this is airdropped to celebrate the Year of the Rabbit, featuring first edition original character, Fuyu.
